    dc:description "FIGURE 17. Species of Veliidae from state of Rio Grande do Norte. (A–B) Platyvelia brachialis, (A) dorsal and (B) ventral views of apterous male. (C–E) Stridulivelia tersa, (C) dorsal and (D) ventral views of micropterous male, (E) lateral view of part of abdomen, white arrows indicate transverse lateral sulci. Scale bars = 1.00 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10017954/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

